          "text": "## Deliverable\n\n**PR:** https://github.com/li-langverse/lic/pull/175 (branch `cursor/httpd-plan-continue`, commit `38d0af3`)\n\n**Plan:** `m15-tls-auto` marked **completed** in `docs/superpowers/plans/2026-05-16-li-httpd-plan.md`\n\n### What shipped\n\n| Area | Implementation |\n|------|----------------|\n| **TOML modes** | `manual`, `self_signed`, `lets_encrypt` (+ shorthand `server.tls = \"…\"`) |\n| **Validation** | Public bind requires TLS; self-signed on public needs `dev=true`; LE needs email + domains matching `server.host`; reserved `/.well-known/acme-challenge/` |\n| **setup-tls** | `scripts/setup-tls-httpd.py` — OpenSSL self-signed; staging/`--dry-run` LE placeholder certs + `acme-account.key` + `acme-renewal.json`; `--renew` |\n| **Runtime** | `runtime/li_rt_httpd.c` parses `[server.tls]`; oracle getters + `m15_tls_oracle.li` |\n| **Flatten** | `tls_mode`, `tls_cert_dir`, `tls_le_*`, `tls_acme_reserved_path`, etc. |\n\n### Tests run\n\n```bash\nexport PYTHONPATH=scripts\n./scripts/check-httpd-tls-auto.sh\nHTTPD_GATES_SKIP_LIC_BUILD=1 ./scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh   # OK\n```\n\nFull `./scripts/httpd-plan-gates.sh` needs **clang** on the host (link step failed here without it); CI should cover `m15_tls_oracle` compile.\n\n### Live sites\n\nNot refreshed (`SKIP_BENCH=1` — no new bench CSV).\n\n### Key files\n\n- `scripts/httpd_tls.py`, `scripts/setup-tls-httpd.py`, `scripts/check-httpd-tls-auto.sh`\n- `li-tests/config_desugar/good/tls_*.toml`, `reject/tls_*.toml`, `li-tests/tls_setup/run_setup_tls.sh`\n- `docs/release-notes/2026-05-22-httpd-m15-tls-auto.md`\n\n**Note:** Production Let's Encrypt HTTP-01 obtain is intentionally gated; use `environment = staging` or `--dry-run` until live ACME challenge wiring lands in M2."
